query:
SELECT p.id, m.title, p.aiModel, p.prediction, p.confidence, p.consensusVote, p.consensusConfidence, p.createdAt
FROM predictions p
JOIN markets m ON p.marketId = m.id
ORDER BY p.createdAt DESC
LIMIT 10
